WEBVTT

00:05.166 --> 00:06.394
Now.

00:06.468 --> 00:09.130
Good people of Locksley,
I have bad news.

00:09.204 --> 00:11.536
Ah, but there is good news as well.

00:11.606 --> 00:14.904
OK, now the bad news is
the Sheriff's taxman is in Clun.

00:14.975 --> 00:19.742
It's not far and he'll be here soon.
But the good news is I, me,

00:19.814 --> 00:23.112
Lucky George,
I'm here with you in Locksley.

00:23.183 --> 00:28.119
Now, I will give you good hard cash
for any jewelry,

00:28.187 --> 00:31.554
trinkets, anything of value,
I will turn to pennies.

00:31.624 --> 00:35.583
Those pennies will pay the taxman and
that will keep you out of the Sheriff's jail.

00:35.661 --> 00:41.827
So help me to help you.
Be lucky, come to Lucky George.

00:41.901 --> 00:45.268
We should have gone round,
I hate these woods.

00:50.475 --> 00:52.466
This, my friends, is an ambush.

00:54.000 --> 01:00.074
